    %% External flows
    User -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>No auth (OAuth at proxy)"| DashRoute
    User -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS passthrough<br/>mTLS client cert"| ClientRoute

    %% Ingress to internal
    DashRoute -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS reencrypt<br/>OpenShift serving cert"| OAuthProxy
    ClientRoute -->|"gRPC/10001<br/>mTLS passthrough<br/>CA-signed cert"| RayHead

    %% Internal flows
    OAuthProxy -->|"HTTP/8265<br/>plaintext<br/>localhost"| Dashboard
    OAuthSvc -->|"HTTPS/8443"| OAuthProxy
    RayHead -->|"gRPC mTLS"| RayWorker
    RayWorker -->|"gRPC/10001 mTLS"| RayHead

