    Operator -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA token"| K8sAPI
    Operator -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA token"| OSConfig
    OAuthProxy -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>OAuth flow"| OAuthServer

    %% API Server to webhook
    K8sAPI -->|"HTTPS/9443<br/>TLS (self-signed)<br/>API server cert"| WebhookSvc

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus["Prometheus"]
    Prometheus -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>plaintext<br/>metrics scrape"| MetricsSvc

